{"tid":1545627,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港警方：修例風波以來共拘捕1187人","createTime":"2019-09-06T03:44:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T14:18:57.000Z","uid":30142,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8a5e87d9605406ebcc852a739d91a8647645020c","tid":1545627,"uid":30142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:44:19.000Z","msg":"香港警方昨日表示，9月4日警方共拘捕4人，均為男子，年齡介乎22至44歲，涉嫌非法集結、襲擊致造成身體傷害、串謀襲擊及非法禁錮等罪名。修例風波至今，香港警方共拘捕1187人。<br />\n  香港警方在5日的例行記者會上表示，8月13日《環球時報》記者付某在香港機場被禁錮和襲擊案，除早前已經被控的3名被捕人士外，警方4日再拘捕一名28歲男子，被控非法禁錮及非法集結罪，已經出庭受審。<br />\n  警方指出，4日晚有暴力分子在港鐵寶琳站破壞閘機，淋潑不明液體，用膠袋套住閉路電視，還有人圍困一名女乘客，襲擊一位港鐵休班職員。當日晚，有暴力分子在旺角警署外聚集，期間有人用激光筆照向警員，並以雜物設置路障，阻塞交通。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/raDFuKk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FraDFuKk.png&h=3cf9f83d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n9月5日，香港警方舉行例行記者會。 香港中通社圖片"},{"pid":"bd3768453494769c4bfef125e505e01773517eb2","tid":1545627,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:45:39.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a719feaab141c31ab8014ef113a7e45cacc7f99","tid":1545627,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:47:54.000Z","msg":"係濫捕，"},{"pid":"0ed8003ebfe61af6458a67a7dfab784a2caefba3","tid":1545627,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a719feaab141c31ab8014ef113a7e45cacc7f99","tid":1545627,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:47:54.000Z","msg":